WEBVTT

00:00.062 --> 00:01.859
<i>Previously on heartland...</i>

00:01.870 --> 00:03.170
<i>I want you to look
at the horse I've just bought.</i>

00:03.238 --> 00:04.572
Zeus is not a liberty horse.

00:04.606 --> 00:07.241
I really think you're going to get
the results you're looking for.

00:07.309 --> 00:08.576
<i>The horse
only needs one master,</i>

00:08.610 --> 00:10.678
so I think Amy's better off
with Zeus on her own.

00:10.713 --> 00:12.179
I'm happy you
said what you said,

00:12.214 --> 00:16.116
because it made me realize
how much I care about you.

00:16.151 --> 00:17.885
You've been drinking again.

00:17.953 --> 00:19.854
You put the horses in danger.

00:19.921 --> 00:21.322
You're fired.

00:21.389 --> 00:22.622
I gotta go. Now?

00:22.657 --> 00:24.091
With the storm,
Amir's freaking out in his stall

00:24.159 --> 00:25.726
and they need me
to settle him down.

00:25.760 --> 00:27.661
Okay, fine. Go.

00:27.695 --> 00:29.396
Fine, I will.

00:29.430 --> 00:31.865
Zeus!

00:31.899 --> 00:33.867
Ungh! Oof!

00:39.841 --> 00:41.408
<i>Blunt force
trauma, heart rate...</i>

00:49.016 --> 00:51.851
The small intestine, yes.

00:58.625 --> 01:00.260
Hello!

01:00.327 --> 01:02.361
Jack.

01:03.430 --> 01:05.598
What?

01:05.665 --> 01:07.266
She's where? She's...

01:07.300 --> 01:08.768
Is she okay?

