<i>come
on, I'll race ya!</i>

07:29.337 --> 07:31.805
Honey, I'm home! Oh.

07:32.507 --> 07:35.376
Oh, gee!

07:35.443 --> 07:37.477
Hey! Wait!

07:38.913 --> 07:42.582
<i>Dr. Foster to O.R.
2. Dr. Foster to O.R. 2.</i>

07:49.257 --> 07:50.891
Ah.

07:56.062 --> 07:58.264
<i>Amy, I'm right here.</i>

07:59.533 --> 08:01.233
Right here.

08:08.875 --> 08:10.509
Any change?

08:12.478 --> 08:14.546
They said she was kicked
in the back of the head.

08:16.349 --> 08:19.751
I can't tell you
how sorry I am.

08:20.954 --> 08:25.024
I feel, in so many ways,
that it's my fault.

08:29.295 --> 08:30.562
I'm still trying
to get to the bottom

08:30.596 --> 08:32.864
of this whole bizarre situation.

08:32.898 --> 08:36.568
My security team is trying to
find out who is responsible.

08:37.503 --> 08:41.573
I have my suspicions,
but nothing I can prove.

08:44.509 --> 08:47.312
Is there anything I can do?

08:55.687 --> 08:57.755
I'm sorry.

09:13.137 --> 09:14.438
<i>You should never
have encouraged Amy</i>

09:14.506 --> 09:15.539
to take that job.

09:15.607 --> 09:16.874
For you,
it was all about the money.

09:16.908 --> 09:17.875
Oh, that is not true.

09:17.909 --> 09:19.109
Amy wanted to go on her own.

09:19.143 --> 09:20.310
I couldn't have stopped her
if I tried.

09:20.345 --> 09:21.678
Yeah, but you didn't try.

09:21.746 --> 09:23.113
<i>Like I said,</i>
<i>you encouraged her.</i>

09:23.181 --> 09:25.983
Please, grandpa, dad,
let's not do this.

09:26.050 --> 09:27.417
- What about Ty, hmm?
- What about Ty?

09:27.451 --> 09:29.019
He never should've let her go
to the stables alone.

09:29.087 --> 09:30.087
He should have gone with her.

09:30.154 --> 09:31.889
Ty isn't Amy's protector.

09:31.923 --> 09:34.624
With a storm coming,
he should have gone.

09:34.658 --> 09:39.362
Ty didn't want her to
go, but Amy said she had to.

09:39.430 --> 09:42.231
I needed Ty to help me
with Phoenix.

09:43.200 --> 09:44.934
It's all my fault.

10:02.085 --> 10:04.453
It's not your fault.

10:06.523 --> 10:08.557
George, it isn't.

10:10.627 --> 10:15.063
You didn't do
anything wrong, okay?

10:19.869 --> 10:21.937
I was mad at Amy.

10:22.972 --> 10:27.708
I made her feel bad that she
wouldn't help with Phoenix.

10:28.978 --> 10:33.048
What if I don't get a chance
to say I'm sorry?

10:34.817 --> 10:36.418
Come here.

10:38.720 --> 10:40.488
No, no, shhh.

10:42.925 --> 10:44.992
Hi. I'm Jenna.

10:45.060 --> 10:46.527
Hi.

10:46.595 --> 10:47.628
Just a heads up.

10:47.663 --> 10:51.499
Dr. Berman wants to do
more tests.

10:51.533 --> 10:52.567
<i>I'm sorry, but you're gonna</i>
<i>have to pop out</i>

10:52.601 --> 10:53.835
<i>when he gets here.</i>

10:53.869 --> 10:58.205
<i>Maybe go to the cafeteria,</i>
<i>or even better,</i>

10:58.239 --> 11:01.241
<i>go outside and get some air.</i>

11:03.044 --> 11:05.412
So you're Amy's fiance?

11:07.648 --> 11:09.383
Yes, I am.

11:10.518 --> 11:13.587
Tests shouldn't take very long.

11:26.934 --> 11:28.767
I'll be right back.

11:29.703 --> 11:31.770
I love you.

11:44.751 --> 11:46.719
Amy. Amy, hey!

11:47.654 --> 11:50.455
Ty?! Ty?! Ty?!

11:51.014 --> 11:53.215
How can you just stand there
telling me

11:53.249 --> 11:55.518
that my daughter
might possibly be blind?

11:55.552 --> 11:57.720
I understand
your distress, Mr. Fleming.

11:57.754 --> 12:01.456
We're doing everything we can to
keep Amy calm and comfortable.

12:01.491 --> 12:04.226
<i>As far as her sight returning,</i>
<i>only time will tell.</i>

12:04.293 --> 12:05.560
<i>This is a brain injury.</i>

12:05.594 --> 12:08.663
<i>We need to know.
We deserve to know.</i>

12:08.731 --> 12:11.233
You've seen these cases before,
what are the odds?

12:11.267 --> 12:13.601
There are no
odds in these situations.

12:13.669 --> 12:15.404
But there has to be
some kind of treatment,

12:15.438 --> 12:17.472
something we can do.

12:20.142 --> 12:21.576
You're gonna be fine, Amy.

12:21.610 --> 12:23.177
I'm not fine, Ty, I'm not fine.

12:23.245 --> 12:27.081
It's okay.
You will be, all right?

12:27.149 --> 12:28.816
<i>Take a breath.</i>

12:29.785 --> 12:32.854
That's good. That's good, Amy.

12:32.922 --> 12:34.422
What happened to me?

12:34.489 --> 12:38.359
You took a hit...
On the back of your head.

12:38.427 --> 12:40.294
From what?

12:40.362 --> 12:42.663
Y-you don't remember?

12:42.697 --> 12:44.098
No.

12:45.967 --> 12:51.838
Amy, the injury affected
the part of your brain

12:51.906 --> 12:54.741
where the vision centre is.

12:54.809 --> 12:57.678
The doctor said this is usually
a temporary state.

12:57.745 --> 12:59.145
Usually?

13:00.848 --> 13:04.184
I'm sorry, Ty, but now that
Amy's a little calmer,

13:04.251 --> 13:05.018
I would like to speak with her.

13:05.086 --> 13:06.453
Yeah, of course.

13:06.520 --> 13:07.787
Hello, young lady.

13:07.821 --> 13:09.556
Hi.

13:09.590 --> 13:12.525
I don't wanna upset you, but do
you think you might be ready now

13:12.593 --> 13:15.095
to answer a few questions
for me?

13:15.162 --> 13:17.363
Okay, good.

13:17.398 --> 13:19.732
Do you remember your name?

13:19.800 --> 13:21.634
Amy Fleming.

13:21.702 --> 13:23.736
Well, that was easy.

13:25.072 --> 13:27.940
Can you tell me what day it is?

13:27.975 --> 13:28.975
I don't know.

13:29.009 --> 13:31.077
Okay, no problem.

13:31.144 --> 13:36.248
Who's this here, this handsome
young man who's holding your hand?

13:36.316 --> 13:39.986
It's Ty borden, my boy-,
my fiance.

13:40.020 --> 13:42.421
Fiance? Hmm. Congratulations.

13:45.024 --> 13:47.392
Do you know why you're here?

13:48.361 --> 13:51.696
Ty said I was in an accident.

13:54.066 --> 13:55.734
My head...

13:55.768 --> 13:58.870
Okay, do you remember
what happened?

13:58.904 --> 14:00.138
No.

14:00.172 --> 14:02.774
Do you remember going
into the stables, Amy?

14:04.343 --> 14:06.344
You have no recollection
at all?

14:06.378 --> 14:07.779
What's the last
thing you remember?

14:07.813 --> 14:11.382
Mr. borden. Ty, please.

14:14.153 --> 14:15.553
It's all right.

14:15.587 --> 14:18.623
Amy, I want you to understand
something, okay?

14:18.657 --> 14:20.224
The way that you're feeling -

14:20.259 --> 14:22.860
<i>the memory loss,</i>
<i>the lack of vision -</i>

14:22.894 --> 14:27.064
<i>is all absolutely normal</i>
<i>after this type of head injury.</i>

14:27.098 --> 14:28.932
I'll come back in a while
and check up on you, okay?

14:28.967 --> 14:32.036
In the meantime,
you get some sleep.

14:34.806 --> 14:36.874
Thank you, doctor,

14:40.945 --> 14:42.345
<i>hey, Ty.</i>

14:44.415 --> 14:47.784
Lou and Tim,
they went home to the girls.

14:47.818 --> 14:49.186
Grandpa.

14:50.321 --> 14:54.957
Yeah. Yeah, it's me.

14:58.496 --> 15:00.297
Ty?

15:00.331 --> 15:01.565
Yeah?

15:01.599 --> 15:04.233
You should go home
and get some rest, I think.

15:04.267 --> 15:05.301
No.

15:07.705 --> 15:09.438
No, I don't need that.

15:09.506 --> 15:11.708
<i>Yeah, you do.</i>

15:11.775 --> 15:18.881
I'll stay here with Amy and I'll
call you if there's any change.

15:18.882 --> 15:20.449
I'm all right.

15:21.984 --> 15:28.990
Ty, you're no good to her if you're
gonna fall apart from exhaustion.

15:30.827 --> 15:32.194
All right.

15:38.334 --> 15:40.035
All right.

15:42.772 --> 15:44.472
Love you.

16:07.529 --> 16:10.464
You're gonna be fine, honey.

16:11.399 --> 16:13.033
You're gonna be fine.

16:20.675 --> 16:22.409
Hmm.

17:14.894 --> 17:17.561
Uh...
Uh, just hold on a second.

17:20.098 --> 17:22.166
Come in.

17:23.769 --> 17:25.537
Hey, Ty. Hey.

17:25.570 --> 17:27.638
You holdin' up all right? Yeah.

17:27.673 --> 17:30.408
We've got some supplies
for you.

17:31.944 --> 17:33.478
How's she doing?

17:33.512 --> 17:35.313
She's, um, she's conscious.

17:36.248 --> 17:38.115
Good. That's really good.

17:38.150 --> 17:40.518
<i>No, it's not...</i>

17:41.487 --> 17:44.689
She's um... She's b-

17:45.491 --> 17:48.092
she's blind.

17:49.862 --> 17:53.630
I know a tonne of guys, they got
tossed off of bulls onto their heads

17:53.665 --> 17:56.667
and they went blind too,
but it's just temporary,

17:56.701 --> 17:59.070
it'll come back. You'll
see, it always comes back.

17:59.104 --> 18:00.304
Yeah.

18:00.339 --> 18:01.939
Is there
anything that we can do?

18:02.007 --> 18:04.575
Anything you want, man,
you name it.

18:04.609 --> 18:06.377
Uh, no, thanks.

18:09.481 --> 18:12.249
I'm just gonna go back
to the hospital.

18:12.283 --> 18:15.686
If you could give Scott a call,
just let him know?

18:15.754 --> 18:16.887
Hey, you got it.

18:16.954 --> 18:18.255
Go. We'll lock up here.

18:18.289 --> 18:19.656
Thanks.

18:26.663 --> 18:31.001
<i>Dr. Martin, dial 256.
