18:49.152 --> 18:50.553
Oh, God.

18:50.621 --> 18:53.423
I'm sorry,
someone should've told you.

18:53.490 --> 18:55.291
No, it's okay.

18:55.358 --> 18:57.059
Come with me. Okay.

