Call me. Okay.

19:33.595 --> 19:35.796
Hey, Amy.

19:35.831 --> 19:36.897
Hey.

19:36.966 --> 19:38.032
- Grandpa?
- Hey. No, it's me.

19:38.067 --> 19:39.100
- Ty, where are you?
- It's me.

19:39.168 --> 19:40.501
I'm right here, I'm right here.

19:40.535 --> 19:42.437
It's okay. It's okay.

19:43.905 --> 19:45.238
Ty, my head.

19:45.306 --> 19:47.274
It's all right. It hurts.

19:47.308 --> 19:50.377
Don't move. Just relax, okay?

19:51.513 --> 19:54.381
Ty, can you tell me
what happened?

19:54.449 --> 19:56.784
Do you remember going
to hill hurst the other night?

19:56.818 --> 19:58.652
No.

19:58.687 --> 20:00.520
There was a storm,
it was pretty bad -

20:00.588 --> 20:02.089
lots of thunder and lightning.

20:02.123 --> 20:04.124
<i>I don't remember.</i>

20:05.059 --> 20:07.127
It's okay. It's okay.

20:10.198 --> 20:12.199
What do you remember?

20:12.233 --> 20:16.970
I think...
I think there was a horse,

20:17.004 --> 20:19.071
but not at heartland.

20:20.107 --> 20:21.240
That's right.

20:22.776 --> 20:24.644
That's right, Amy.

20:24.678 --> 20:27.680
You had a new job
at hill hurst.

20:27.715 --> 20:31.117
You were working
with a new horse, Zeus.

20:32.285 --> 20:33.585
Zeus.

20:33.653 --> 20:37.556
And, the night before last,
you went back to help out

20:37.590 --> 20:39.591
and you had an accident.

20:39.626 --> 20:41.960
<i>They found you</i>
<i>in the main stables.</i>

20:41.995 --> 20:43.062
<i>The doctors think</i>
<i>that you were kicked</i>

20:43.130 --> 20:45.531
<i>in the back of the head
by one of the horses.</i>

20:49.369 --> 20:50.769
Ty! Hey, hey.

20:51.804 --> 20:53.271
Hey, I'm right here,
I'm right here.

20:53.305 --> 20:56.341
I'm so scared.

20:56.375 --> 20:58.777
I've never been so scared
in my life.

20:58.811 --> 21:00.512
Shh... it's okay.

21:00.547 --> 21:03.682
Hey, we're going to be okay.

21:03.716 --> 21:05.651
You're going to get better,
okay?

21:07.886 --> 21:09.854
It's okay.

21:09.922 --> 21:12.190
Got to be something
that doctor can do.

21:12.224 --> 21:13.658
Jack?

21:13.692 --> 21:16.494
How can it be good enough
to just sit and wait?

21:16.529 --> 21:17.995
Time will tell, he says.

21:18.064 --> 21:19.030
Come on, what is that?

21:19.098 --> 21:20.265
That is ridiculous.

21:20.299 --> 21:22.233
We need a second opinion,
we need it pronto.

21:22.301 --> 21:23.668
<i>Tim, calm down.</i>

21:23.702 --> 21:25.803
<i>I am calm, we just
have to do something.</i>

21:28.774 --> 21:30.174
How is she?

21:33.879 --> 21:36.180
Uh, she's sleeping.

21:36.214 --> 21:41.085
Look, Dr. Berman is one of
the top neurologists in alberta.

21:41.152 --> 21:43.687
<i>I know it's tough</i>
<i>to just wait and see,</i>

21:43.754 --> 21:45.089
<i>but she's in good hands</i>

21:45.156 --> 21:47.023
<i>and it's the only thing</i>
<i>we can do.</i>

21:47.092 --> 21:49.359
<i>No, it isn't.
She can't see.</i>

21:49.427 --> 21:50.627
<i>We need a better doctor.</i>

21:50.661 --> 21:52.762
<i>We need to move her</i>
<i>to a better hospital.</i>

21:52.830 --> 21:55.265
No, we need to bring her home.

21:56.533 --> 22:00.570
What, and do without the only
medical help we're getting?

22:01.772 --> 22:03.673
Look, I know Amy.

22:03.741 --> 22:06.743
She's completely disoriented
in that hospital.

22:06.811 --> 22:08.411
She's gonna get better
a lot quicker if she's here,

22:08.479 --> 22:10.647
in a place
that she's familiar with.

22:10.715 --> 22:12.448
We need to bring her home.

22:12.516 --> 22:14.484
I'm sorry, Ty, but I
think that she's better off

22:14.518 --> 22:15.485
in the hospital for now.

22:15.519 --> 22:17.587
I have to agree.

22:18.688 --> 22:22.258
Well, I don't. I don't agree.

22:24.060 --> 22:26.462
I have to get
some of her things.

22:59.061 --> 23:02.630
Ty?! Ty! Where are you?!

23:02.665 --> 23:03.731
It-it's all right, Amy.

23:03.766 --> 23:05.366
Ty? It's all right.

23:05.400 --> 23:07.001
Where is he? Just calm down.

23:07.069 --> 23:09.671
Just breathe. Breathe.

23:09.705 --> 23:11.873
- Just breathe.
- Oh no!

23:11.907 --> 23:13.775
You're okay.

23:13.809 --> 23:15.710
<i>You're safe.</i>

23:15.744 --> 23:18.112
<i>It's okay.</i>

23:31.193 --> 23:32.793
Hello?

23:32.827 --> 23:33.760
<i>Hello, this nurse Jenna
calling from the bow hospital.</i>

23:33.795 --> 23:35.028
<i>Is this Ty borden?</i>

23:35.063 --> 23:36.362
Yes.

23:36.397 --> 23:38.065
<i>Amy Fleming has
been asking for you.</i>

23:38.099 --> 23:39.199
Is she okay?

23:39.233 --> 23:41.001
<i>She's quite agitated and-</i>

23:41.035 --> 23:42.302
yeah, okay, I'm coming now.

23:42.336 --> 23:43.970
Yeah, I'm leaving right now.

23:47.308 --> 23:48.274
Hi.

23:48.309 --> 23:49.976
I gave her a mild sedative.

23:50.011 --> 23:51.344
Buzz me if you need me.

23:51.378 --> 23:52.679
Okay.

23:54.114 --> 23:56.782
Amy. Hey, hey, hey.

23:56.817 --> 23:57.917
Ty!

23:57.951 --> 23:59.285
I'm right here. Right here.

23:59.320 --> 24:01.321
Are you okay?

24:01.355 --> 24:03.323
I'm so scared.

24:03.357 --> 24:06.359
I don't know where I am.
I hate this.

24:06.393 --> 24:07.760
I'm right here.

24:09.662 --> 24:12.297
I just want to go home.

24:12.332 --> 24:15.367
Please take me home. Please.

24:23.143 --> 24:25.076
<i>So you've done some research.</i>

24:25.111 --> 24:27.078
What did you find? Thank you.

24:27.113 --> 24:30.382
I've read a tonne of articles that
say stress can be a key factor,

24:30.450 --> 24:31.683
and the more stress
that Amy is under,

24:31.751 --> 24:33.619
the less likely it is
that her vision will improve.

24:33.686 --> 24:36.020
Stress can be a factor,
yes, that's true.

24:36.088 --> 24:37.789
Well, she is stressed here.
Completely stressed.

24:37.857 --> 24:39.224
She had a panic attack
last night.

24:39.292 --> 24:43.261
That is completely understandable
given the circumstances, Ty.

24:43.295 --> 24:46.064
Well, I've also read that blindness
can be purely psychological,

24:46.098 --> 24:48.432
caused by a traumatic event.

24:48.500 --> 24:50.835
There was trauma. Blunt trauma.

24:50.903 --> 24:54.239
This is not psychological,
this is physical.

24:54.306 --> 24:56.808
I'm sorry, Ty, but I've got very
little patience for websites

24:56.876 --> 24:57.941
and self-diagnosis.

24:58.009 --> 25:00.043
Okay, look. Wait.

25:02.414 --> 25:04.482
If there are medical reasons
that are keeping her here

25:04.516 --> 25:11.989
that I don't know about, I respect
that, I do, but if there aren't,

25:12.056 --> 25:13.991
what's the difference
between her lying here

25:14.058 --> 25:15.492
and her lying in her own bed?

25:15.559 --> 25:17.227
She can be monitored here.

25:17.295 --> 25:19.162
She has twenty-four hour care
here.

25:19.229 --> 25:20.497
I can monitor her.

25:20.531 --> 25:22.399
I can watch her,
twenty-four seven.

25:22.433 --> 25:25.067
And we have a family doctor
five minutes away.

25:25.135 --> 25:31.140
Please, she'll get
better faster, at home.

25:31.208 --> 25:33.242
I know her.

25:57.434 --> 25:58.834
We're home.

26:07.970 --> 26:11.138
<i>Dr. Berman said</i>
<i>to keep the room dark.</i>

26:11.172 --> 26:13.240
Not that it matters.

26:14.710 --> 26:18.980
Hey, come on, Amy,
it's gonna change.

26:19.014 --> 26:21.448
Now that you're home, it will.

26:24.652 --> 26:25.986
Here.

26:27.288 --> 26:29.256
I got you some orange juice.

26:34.162 --> 26:35.129
- Oh!
- I got it, I got it.

26:35.163 --> 26:36.563
Damn.

26:36.597 --> 26:38.832
It's okay. It's okay.

26:38.866 --> 26:41.134
Okay, you just need to relax.

26:41.168 --> 26:43.236
Relax, okay? Lay back.

26:44.271 --> 26:46.006
Get some rest.

26:50.144 --> 26:53.146
You're gonna get better,
all right?

26:53.180 --> 26:56.115
You're gonna see again.

26:56.150 --> 26:58.817
And what if I don't?

26:58.885 --> 27:00.953
What if I can't see, Ty?

27:01.888 --> 27:03.089
What if I can't see you
ever again?!

27:03.123 --> 27:04.957
Shh, shh. Shh.

27:05.926 --> 27:07.326
Shhh...

27:09.396 --> 27:11.797
You will.

27:14.167 --> 27:16.234
You will.

27:21.975 --> 27:23.075
Bad idea.

27:23.142 --> 27:24.276
Who gave you permission
to bring her home?

27:24.310 --> 27:26.579
Dr. Berman did.
It's the best thing for Amy.

27:26.613 --> 27:28.146
Well, you and the doctor
are both wrong.

27:28.214 --> 27:29.614
This is a family decision.

27:29.682 --> 27:30.615
I am family.

27:30.683 --> 27:33.085
We know that, Ty, we do, but
dad's not entirely wrong.

27:33.152 --> 27:35.187
I wish you had
talked to us first.

27:38.958 --> 27:40.892
<i>I'm sorry to barge in.</i>

27:40.960 --> 27:42.794
I just came from the hospital.

27:42.828 --> 27:46.998
They told me about...
Her sight,

27:47.066 --> 27:48.866
and Amy is home.

27:48.934 --> 27:49.934
I am surprised.

27:49.969 --> 27:51.836
So are we.

27:51.904 --> 27:54.405
<i>But that's good.</i>

27:54.473 --> 27:56.574
Does that mean there is change
for the better?

27:56.642 --> 27:58.042
No. No change.

27:58.978 --> 28:00.177
<i>All right.</i>

28:00.245 --> 28:02.179
I want to make you an offer.

28:03.148 --> 28:04.948
I have a jet.

28:05.016 --> 28:07.518
Understand that
it's at your disposal.

28:07.586 --> 28:09.520
<i>I can get Amy</i>
<i>to the best specialist</i>

28:09.588 --> 28:12.656
<i>in the country, in the
world if need be.</i>

28:12.690 --> 28:14.658
Thank you, that is so generous.

28:14.726 --> 28:15.659
Yeah, we should do it.

28:15.727 --> 28:17.328
Just wait a second.

28:17.395 --> 28:20.764
Ahmed, that's a very
generous offer, thank you,

28:20.798 --> 28:23.566
but ultimately
this is Amy's decision.

28:26.971 --> 28:29.039
Just let me know.

28:38.015 --> 28:39.982
I don't want to. I
don't want to go anywhere.

28:40.050 --> 28:42.818
No,
Lou, I don't want to leave, okay?

28:42.853 --> 28:45.021
This is the only place that
feels certain to me right now.

28:45.055 --> 28:46.289
Are you sure?

28:46.323 --> 28:47.923
Amy, it could change everything,
it could-

28:47.958 --> 28:50.793
no, I don't want
to talk about it.

28:50.861 --> 28:52.728
We just want
what's best for you,

28:52.763 --> 28:56.265
and I would never forgive
<i>myself if you-<i>Amy: Don't.</i></i>

28:56.299 --> 29:02.705
It feels good to be home
right now, to be my own bed.

29:02.739 --> 29:05.141
At least I know where I am.

29:06.609 --> 29:10.546
Okay. I'll call Ahmed and tell
him we appreciate his offer,

29:10.580 --> 29:13.715
but we're not going to go
with it.

29:21.591 --> 29:25.359
Hey, I've been
looking all over for you.

29:26.295 --> 29:29.363
Amy's home.
Did you hear anything?

29:29.398 --> 29:31.132
No, nothing.

29:32.068 --> 29:33.835
What's the matter?

29:33.869 --> 29:35.403
It's like you've been hiding
from me.

29:38.140 --> 29:41.742
I just don't want
to get used to this.

29:41.776 --> 29:43.578
Used to what?

29:43.612 --> 29:49.617
Us. It's been feeling too good, too
like it used to - the old days.

29:49.651 --> 29:51.652
I just, I can't go there

29:51.687 --> 29:52.953
because it's probably
going to go away again

29:52.987 --> 29:56.056
and I know I can't handle that.

29:57.759 --> 30:00.027
I'm not going anywhere.

30:01.562 --> 30:04.297
It feels right for me too.

30:05.433 --> 30:07.467
There's a reason
that I came back

30:07.501 --> 30:11.671
and it wasn't to check
on my mother's house.

30:11.706 --> 30:13.773
It was to see you.

30:20.448 --> 30:22.482
Uh...

30:25.786 --> 30:28.688
Hey. So? You call him? Ahmed?

30:28.756 --> 30:30.056
Yeah, I called him.

30:30.090 --> 30:32.825
Good boy. Okay, so we're on.

30:32.860 --> 30:34.460
No, we're not.

30:35.395 --> 30:37.563
What do you mean?

30:37.631 --> 30:39.065
I turned him down.

30:39.133 --> 30:40.967
Are you out of your mind?

30:41.001 --> 30:42.668
Do you realize that
he's the difference

30:42.702 --> 30:44.771
between Amy being blind
and Amy being able to see?

30:44.838 --> 30:46.472
Tim, it's not that simple.

30:46.539 --> 30:48.073
Besides, it's Amy's decision.

30:48.141 --> 30:49.808
No, Amy can't make a decision.

30:49.876 --> 30:52.378
Then I made the decision, okay?
I'm her fiance.

30:52.445 --> 30:54.212
I'm not some stable boy
you can push around.

30:54.247 --> 30:56.348
- I don't care who the hell you think you are.
- Don't touch me!

30:56.416 --> 30:58.751
You guys! Dad! Stop!

30:58.818 --> 31:01.119
You had no right
to make that decision.

31:01.187 --> 31:02.354
Well, I made it!

31:02.422 --> 31:03.621
Give me his number,
I'm gonna call the guy.

31:03.656 --> 31:04.555
Okay, would you
both just simmer down?

31:04.623 --> 31:05.957
Amy is trying to sleep.

31:05.992 --> 31:07.525
Amy is gonna do
far better here recovering

31:07.593 --> 31:09.560
than she is with the stress
of getting on some plane.

31:09.628 --> 31:10.829
Are you an expert now?

31:10.897 --> 31:12.664
I'm not saying I'm
an expert on this.

31:12.731 --> 31:14.499
Well, that's good,
because you're not.

31:15.835 --> 31:16.601
<i>Understand
the situation, Tim.</i>

31:17.736 --> 31:18.736
You don't know
what you're doing!

31:18.771 --> 31:19.771
What do you know?

31:21.707 --> 31:22.840
"Research."

31:22.908 --> 31:24.375
Would you just both stop?!
Amy is sleeping!

31:24.443 --> 31:25.510
What is going on?

31:25.577 --> 31:26.911
He... he just...

31:28.046 --> 31:29.414
<i>Ruined any chance we have</i>

31:29.448 --> 31:31.982
of getting the best medical
attention at our disposal.

31:36.454 --> 31:38.856
It wasn't just Ty.
Amy didn't want to go.

31:38.924 --> 31:41.991
Amy can't make a decision
for herself!

31:42.059 --> 31:44.093
Ty?

31:46.263 --> 31:48.965
Ty, I think
I remember something.

31:56.533 --> 31:58.200
<i>There was this</i>
<i>massive horse fight</i>

31:58.235 --> 31:59.802
and all the stall doors
were open.

31:59.836 --> 32:03.039
But, Ty, it wasn't just a dream,
this is what actually happened.

32:03.073 --> 32:04.941
There was something else.

32:04.975 --> 32:06.375
There was someone there.

32:06.410 --> 32:09.345
In my dream,
I saw someone running.

32:09.379 --> 32:11.013
I couldn't see their face.

32:13.616 --> 32:16.618
Okay. Amy, you should lie down.

32:16.653 --> 32:20.989
Ty, I am so tired
of lying here.

32:23.760 --> 32:26.061
Feeling any better, Amy?

32:26.095 --> 32:28.163
Hey, Georgie.

32:29.698 --> 32:32.167
Yeah, a little better.

32:32.201 --> 32:36.271
Well, do you want to go out
to the barn to see Phoenix?

32:37.906 --> 32:41.076
I'm sorry,
I didn't mean to say that.

32:41.110 --> 32:42.510
It's okay.

32:42.544 --> 32:44.579
I don't think she's feeling
up to it right now, Georgie.

32:44.613 --> 32:48.683
Actually, I would love
to go out to the barn.

32:53.088 --> 32:55.155
Here we are, Amy.

32:58.961 --> 33:00.327
This is stupid.
I can't do this.

33:00.362 --> 33:03.630
Hey, hey, hey.
Okay, we can go back.

33:03.664 --> 33:05.065
Do you want to go back?

33:06.834 --> 33:09.036
No. No?

33:09.104 --> 33:11.438
It's okay.

33:11.473 --> 33:13.540
All right, right here.

33:18.779 --> 33:20.446
Here's Phoenix.

33:20.481 --> 33:21.447
He's right here, Amy.

33:21.482 --> 33:23.316
Hey, buddy. Look, it's Amy.

33:27.221 --> 33:29.656
Hey, hey, hey, easy. You okay?

33:33.227 --> 33:36.295
Yeah, I want to go to spartan.

33:37.331 --> 33:39.965
Okay, he's right up here.

33:44.638 --> 33:47.873
Hi.

33:47.908 --> 33:49.808
Hey, spartan.

33:49.843 --> 33:51.610
You're such a good boy.

33:57.450 --> 33:59.652
You got better for me,

34:01.054 --> 34:04.623
I'm gonna get better for you,
okay?

34:04.691 --> 34:06.725
I promise.

34:18.571 --> 34:21.540
Adrian. It was Adrian
in the stable that night.

34:21.607 --> 34:24.976
I saw him running away.

34:25.010 --> 34:29.513
I suspected it was Adrian all
along, but I had no proof.

34:29.581 --> 34:32.315
The security cameras couldn't
pick up anything in the darkness,

34:32.350 --> 34:35.252
so we had no recorded
image available.

34:36.254 --> 34:37.889
I have the local police
tracking him down

34:37.956 --> 34:40.991
and then we'll get
some answers.

34:41.926 --> 34:45.629
So it was Adrian that
texted you, not Ahmed.

34:45.663 --> 34:48.732
I had completely forgotten
until now.

34:50.135 --> 34:52.168
He did it deliberately, then?

34:53.138 --> 34:54.472
He set me up?

34:55.773 --> 34:57.574
Why would he do that?

34:58.610 --> 35:01.011
He had begun to drink again.

35:01.079 --> 35:07.217
That's why I fired him, and this
was his revenge on me, I suppose.

35:07.251 --> 35:11.321
I am so sorry
that he took it out on you.

35:19.530 --> 35:22.665
Feeling better? Less pain?

35:22.699 --> 35:24.434
Yeah.

35:26.737 --> 35:28.804
Whatcha thinkin' about?

35:30.140 --> 35:31.874
Just that...

35:35.478 --> 35:41.517
I still can't see and I
probably won't ever again.

35:41.551 --> 35:45.354
Amy, you will.

35:45.388 --> 35:47.789
I know it, you will.

35:47.823 --> 35:55.030
You know I've had a lot of time
to think, probably too much.

35:55.064 --> 36:00.869
And there is a good chance
that I won't get better,

36:00.903 --> 36:02.003
and that I'll be blind.

36:02.071 --> 36:03.872
No. Ty, please listen.

36:05.374 --> 36:09.878
Look, you didn't sign up
for this,

36:11.013 --> 36:12.647
and you don't need
to follow through.

36:12.682 --> 36:15.116
I'm not going to hold you
to any promise.

36:15.151 --> 36:18.352
What are you talking about?

36:18.387 --> 36:22.156
I just want you
to think about it.

36:23.158 --> 36:27.795
Amy, I don't need
to think about it.

36:27.862 --> 36:31.765
We're engaged,
and we're gonna get married.

36:31.833 --> 36:36.303
I'm here for you no matter
what, I promise you.

36:37.238 --> 36:42.776
And if anything, this whole thing
has made me love you even more.

36:44.946 --> 36:49.416
It's made me realize
how precious our time is

36:49.450 --> 36:51.618
and how we shouldn't waste it.

36:52.553 --> 36:53.920
Any of it.

38:11.275 --> 38:14.109
You have the greenest eyes.

38:56.685 --> 39:00.087
Yes, her vision is improving
by the minute.

39:01.489 --> 39:05.293
<i>We'll bring her in to see you,</i>
<i>absolutely.</i>

39:05.327 --> 39:07.661
<i>Thank you, doctor, thank you.</i>

39:07.729 --> 39:10.030
<i>That's what she said.</i>

39:10.965 --> 39:12.499
<i>Yeah, no, it's amazing.</i>

39:12.534 --> 39:15.502
We're all just so,
so happy here.

39:15.570 --> 39:17.070
Okay, I'll see you soon.

